	<h1 class="title">顶级VC告诉你，如何像包装明星一样做科技风险投资</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Noam Scheiber</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-05 07:45:49 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9146/medium/9146.jpg?1436688052" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


